INSERT INTO elections (
            id,
            server_id,
            client_id,
            machine_id,
            election_hash,
            definition
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT (machine_id, client_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            server_id = $2,
            election_hash = $5,
            definition = $6
